---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section class="founder" id="founder">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="founder-grid">
      <div class="founder-copy reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> The founder</span>
        <h2>Built From the Bay,<br/>Not a Boardroom.</h2>

        <p>
          I started Fitchin Automotive Detailing &amp; Window Tinting from nothing.
          In the beginning I was close to all of it — the work, the customers, the quotes, the messages.
        </p>
        <p>
          Over time I trained the team to handle the install side and stepped out completely.
          That freed me up to focus on what was actually keeping the business growing: the marketing.
          The website. The service pages. The quote flow. The Google presence.
          The way customers found us and trusted us before they ever called.
        </p>
        <p>
          Designed to Elevate is the system I built for Fitchin, now offered to other service-business owners.
          I’m not a marketer who learned from theory. I’m a service-business owner who had to figure marketing
          out in the real world to keep my own shop growing.
        </p>

        <ul class="principles" role="list">
          <li><span class="mark" aria-hidden="true"></span> Clear beats clever. Every time.</li>
          <li><span class="mark" aria-hidden="true"></span> Pretty isn’t the point — clarity is.</li>
          <li><span class="mark" aria-hidden="true"></span> Plain over polished. True over generic.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <aside class="founder-card reveal" aria-label="About the founder">
        <div class="card-inner">
          <div class="badge">
            <img src={`${base}logo-mark.png`} alt="" width="64" height="64" />
          </div>
          <p class="quote">
            “I’m not coming at this from theory. I’m coming at it from inside the kind of business I help.”
          </p>
          <div class="meta">
            <div class="meta-row">
              <span class="label">Based</span>
              <span>Zanesville, Ohio</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-row">
              <span class="label">Working</span>
              <span>With service businesses anywhere</span>
            </div>
            <div class="meta-row">
              <span class="label">Background</span>
              <span>Founder of Fitchin Auto Detailing &amp; Window Tinting</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .founder-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.4fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .founder-copy h2 { margin: 18px 0 24px; }
  .founder-copy p { color: var(--soft); max-width: 60ch; }
  .principles {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .principles li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: rgba(17,21,30,0.6);
    color: var(--white);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .founder-card {
    position: sticky;
    top: 100px;
  }
  .card-inner {
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--ink-2), var(--ink-3));
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card-inner::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px; right: -120px;
    width: 280px; height: 280px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(30,72,255,0.18), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .badge {
    width: 64px; height: 64px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--white);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .badge img { width: 64px; height: 64px; object-fit: contain; }
  .quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .meta { display: grid; gap: 14px; }
  .meta-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .meta-row:last-child { border-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; }
  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--mute);
    align-self: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .founder-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .founder-card { position: static; }
  }
</style>
